1.Name: CustomLocalizedMessageProductNameAndFlowNameAtSameTime
1.Description: Error message to inform it is not possible to search by ProductName and FlowName at the same time.
1.en-US: It is not possible to search by ProductName and FlowName at the same time.

2.Name: CustomLocalizedMessageProductNameOrFlowNameNotDefined
2.Description: Error message to inform that the ProductName or FlowName is not defined.
2.en-US: It is not possible to search if ProductName or FlowName is not defined on Input.

3.Name: CustomLocalizedMessageFlowVersionWithoutFlowName
3.Description: Error message to inform that it is not possible to set FlowVersion without FlowName.
3.en-US: It is not possible to search by FlowVersion if there is no FlowName defined on Input.

4.Name: CustomLocalizedMessageProductHasNoFlowPath
4.Description: Error message to inform that the Product has no FlowPath defined.
4.en-US: The Product has no associated FlowPath.

5.Name: CustomLocalizedMessageCustomFlowInformationToERPDataObjectNull
5.Description: Error message to inform about CustomFlowInformationToERPData has no data.
5.en-US: No data to return in XML message.
